379
00:34:20,910 --> 00:34:25,350
  But how come I started seeing a ghost all of a sudden?

380
00:34:26,470 --> 00:34:29,950
  Is having hallucinations a symptom of a brain tumor?

381
00:34:29,950 --> 00:34:32,030
  Is he a ghost or am I seeing things?

382
00:34:32,030 --> 00:34:33,660
- That's better. 
 - What?

383
00:34:33,660 --> 00:34:35,530
Think of me as a hallucination.

384
00:34:35,530 --> 00:34:37,160
All right. What?

385
00:34:40,660 --> 00:34:43,200
What? Did you just read my mind?

386
00:34:43,200 --> 00:34:45,160
Not much of reading, but it's more like listening.

387
00:34:45,160 --> 00:34:47,050
Why would you listen to my thoughts like that?

388
00:34:47,050 --> 00:34:51,910
