399
00:35:40,650 --> 00:35:42,400
Even if you tell others about me,

400
00:35:42,400 --> 00:35:45,560
people will think you're just seeing things because you're sick.

401
00:35:45,560 --> 00:35:48,000
Just keep your mouth shut.

402
00:35:48,000 --> 00:35:51,600
What! Wait a minute. Hey!

403
00:35:54,080 --> 00:35:56,210
How can a man be that annoying?

