00:37:14,150 --> 00:37:16,110
It was my fault.

414
00:37:16,110 --> 00:37:17,920
It was my fault!

415
00:37:17,920 --> 00:37:21,090
Please forgive me. Please forgive me.

416
00:37:21,090 --> 00:37:25,690
I told you countless times, and you never listened to me.

417
00:37:26,900 --> 00:37:29,270
No, no! It was my fault! It was my fault!

418
00:37:29,270 --> 00:37:32,560
No! No! It was my fault! No!

